Where are you going?

219
00:15:11,077 --> 00:15:13,538
I'm coming! Just a minute!

220
00:15:15,498 --> 00:15:16,999
It's our girls' day out.

221
00:15:18,751 --> 00:15:19,585
Here!

222
00:15:19,669 --> 00:15:21,003
