goes beyond the fracture itself.

247
00:16:37,246 --> 00:16:38,456
I like your explanation.

248
00:16:41,876 --> 00:16:43,794
Mercedes really was a ballet dancer?

249
00:16:45,880 --> 00:16:48,883
