<i>Dad!</i>

973
01:04:25,278 --> 01:04:26,654
<i>Look how high I can jump!</i>

974
01:04:26,738 --> 01:04:28,907
<i>I can touch the sky. Yeah!</i>

975
01:04:30,408 --> 01:04:32,827
<i>I always have energy, I never run out.</i>

976
01:04:35,163 --> 01:04:36,414
<i>I love you, Dad.</i>

977
